What else do you want to know?

41
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:18,930
Aren't you...

42
00:04:20,190 --> 00:04:22,210
going to leave?

43
00:04:23,610 --> 00:04:26,990
I will. Once you're asleep.

44
00:04:34,290 --> 00:04:36,880
Marriage? Eun Ho.

45
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:39,400
I'm not doing that.

46
00:04:40,230 --> 00:04:42,680
I'm not doing that stuff, Eun Ho.

47
