You said you weren't going to.

51
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:08,720
Yes, you did. Several times.

52
00:05:13,110 --> 00:05:15,680
I told you that at the beginning.

53
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:18,100
I'm not doing that kind of thing.

54
00:05:18,100 --> 00:05:20,120
- So-
- I know.

55
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:28,300
But you know, I understood that for the first few years.

56
00:05:28,300 --> 00:05:31,960
But Jung Hyun Oh, we've been dating for eight years.

57
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:36,600
If you really didn't want to marry me, you didn't need to date me for eight years.

58
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:39,240
You should've broken up with me at a reasonable point, in a reasonable place,

59
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,860
with some reasonable words. No?

60
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:54,200
Even if I started seeing someone right now, I'd be married after 40.

61
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:14,480
No.

62
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:17,060
I don't think it'll take that long.

63
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,990
What?

64
00:06:23,330 --> 00:06:26,350
If you want to meet someone now, we should break up now.

65
00:06:29,270 --> 00:06:31,460
Hey, Jung Hyun Oh.

66
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:39,440
Bye, Ju Eun Ho.

67
00:06:42,270 --> 00:06:43,900
Hey, are you serious?

68
00:06:43,900 --> 00:06:46,490
You're actually breaking up with me like this?

69
00:06:48,110 --> 00:06:50,340
Then how should I do it?

70
00:06:52,870 --> 00:06:55,470
This isn't it, Hyun Oh. We've been together for eight years...

71
00:06:55,470 --> 00:06:56,980
Exactly.

72
00:06:56,980 --> 00:06:59,530
So, how should we break up?

73
00:07:01,060 --> 00:07:03,640
Don't you know what eight years mean?

74
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:06,120
It takes a child to be born and start elementary school in that time.

75
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:09,640
We're breaking up like this after all that time? In one breath?

76
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:12,620
It's not like we were just messing around!

77
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:19,750
Whether we've been together for eight years or eight weeks,

78
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:23,530
breakups are the same.

79
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:28,410
Goodbye. So long.

80
00:07:28,410 --> 00:07:31,680
That's the end of it, Eun Ho.

81
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:18,010
